        "text": "=Write a short, friendly WhatsApp follow-up (maximum 55 words) for a qualified real estate lead.\n\nLead Details:\n- Name: {{ $json.lead_data.name }}\n- Preferred Location: {{ $json.lead_data.preferred_location }}\n- Budget: {{ $json.lead_data.budget }}\n\nInstructions:\n- Thank them for their enquiry.\n- Mention that matching properties have been shortlisted.\n- Invite them for a site visit this week.\n- Ask them to reply \"YES\" to book.\n- Keep it natural and conversational.\n- Do NOT use emojis.\n- Return ONLY the WhatsApp message text.",
